*Ko* će otići na odmor? (Who will go on vacation?)
Moje *ko* se zove Mihajlo. (My *cow* is called Mihajlo.)
Ona je ušla u sobu u ko*joj* je čula glas. (She entered the room in *which* she heard a voice.)
*Ko* god da je, neka se javi. (Whoever it is, let them come forward.)
*Ko* god da je učinio to, mora da se kazni. (Whoever *did* it, must be punished.)